iry, logout invalidation) directly affects whether an authorization check can proceed; an expired session must not grant admin access.\",\n          \"relation_hint\": \"impacts\",\n          \"target_section_id\": \"docs/spec/auth.md#0004-authorization\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"search_keys\": [\n        \"session management\",\n        \"secure login cookie\",\n        \"cookie marked http only\",\n        \"cookie marked secure\",\n        \"session expiration\",\n        \"logout invalidates session\",\n        \"login session timeout\",\n        \"Authentication Specification\",\n        \"Session Management\"\n      ],\n      \"semantic_hash\": \"a0ceaff86194b771e051919788cb42c930b9c083b2698ac1dd266c0ff75b9410\",\n      \"source_document_id\": \"docs/spec/auth.md\",\n      \"source_hash\": \"433a68ab1268046b860e4ebc95610c013644f085a6de9c330a8ad037c115736b\",\n      \"source_section_id\": \"docs/spec/auth.md#0002-session-management\",\n      \"source_span\": {\n        \"end_line\": 6,\n        \"end_offset\": 156,\n        \"start_line\": 3,\n        \"start_offset\": 54\n      },\n      \"stable_chunk_uid\": \"460e35e7c95721e5\",\n      \"stable_section_uid\": \"460e35e7c95721e5\",\n      \"summary\": \"Describes session cookie handling after login, including secure cookie flags, default timeout, and immediate invalidation on logout.\",\n      \"text\": \"Authentication Specification / Session Management | Describes session cookie handling after login, including secure cookie flags, default timeout, and immediate invalidation on logout. | session management secure login cookie cookie marked http only cookie marked secure session expiration logout invalidates session login session timeout Authentication Specification | HttpOnly\"\n    },\n    \"docs/spec/auth.md#0003-csrf-protection\": {\n      \"heading_path\": [\n        \"Authentication Specification\",\n        \"CSRF Protection\"\n      ],\n      \"identifiers\": [\n        \"CSRF\",\n        \"POST\