ms`、classification LLM calls 2、cache hit 19、`high_priority_skipped_count=0`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:26:- artifact: `.spec-grag/runs/20260502T081601.899646Z-spec-inject-7b71d453395a.json`、`.spec-grag/runs/20260502T081700.397111Z-spec-inject-925565b62f5d.json`、`.spec-grag/runs/20260502T082150.417804Z-spec-realign-fd72d9ad2316.json`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:63:- `cli.py` の inject / realign 共通 readiness + injection pipeline を `run_injection_pipeline()` に抽出した\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:64:- foreground `/spec-core` と dirty/stale 時の inject / realign core update は watcher と `WatchLock` を共有し、lock 取得不可なら `watcher_processing` blocked にする\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:78:- Answer cache: miss `.spec-grag/runs/20260502T154645.565178Z-spec-realign-d0c0cfd9dbbf.json` は answer `38,386ms` / LLM 1 call。hit `.spec-grag/runs/20260502T154702.759380Z-spec-realign-5aaef0f12cff.json` は answer `2.886ms` / LLM 0 call / `answer_cache_hit=true`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:104:- 実装済み: JSON protocol / CLI transport / manifest reconciliation / strict config validation / production policy validation / smoke explicit mode / embedding metadata + rebuild guard / Ollama embedding provider 接続 / embedding provider fail-fast / conservative grounding scoring / Classification LLM mode + fail-fast / Codex CLI adapter / Claude CLI adapter / adapter retry・backoff・timeout・schema repair / extraction schema / provenance-based stale delete / vector retrieval pattern / 4 軸 transient annotation / CLI 出力の local schema validation / sidecar artifacts / sidecar corruption recovery / Concept diff pending-apply protocol / LLM Concept diff proposal + fail-fast / Core Concept index / Concept diff 候補生成 / `/spec-core` E2E / `/spec-inject` / `/spec-realign` / 外部契約 E2E / schema LLM extraction path の `/spec-core` 接続 / Codex・Claude 実機 smoke / Core Concept index retrieval / raw document chunk sidecar / raw chunk dense vector index / BM25 sparse lexical index / QueryPlan / hybrid chunk retrieval + RRF / raw chunk evidence InjectionContext / ChapterAnchor・cluster retrieval 統合 / Conflict validator deterministic rule pack / Agentic search 複数 request・excerpt validation / AgenticSearchCandidate source_span strict validation / Answer LLM provider config / Answer prompt + structured schema / Answer partial recovery / Answer phase NeedMoreContext block / ConflictNotes・ReviewNotes 可視化 / slash wrapper / CLI fixture / run artifact provider summary / smoke scripts / active templates / Codex command templates / project setup / system setup / fresh project smoke\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:117:| `spec_grag/cli.py` | stdin JSON -> stdout JSON の CLI entrypoint。`/spec-core` / `/spec-inject` / `/spec-realign` を dispatch |\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:129:| `spec_grag/realign.py` | Answer phase isolation 境界。`task_prompt + InjectionContext` だけを入力に、template fallback または Codex / Claude Answer LLM provider で 4 区分回答を生成 |\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:135:| `tests/` | protocol / CLI / fixture / manifest / adapter / extraction / graph ops / retrieval / sidecar / concept index / concept diff / core E2E / schema extraction / inject-realign / external contract E2E / Phase 6 operations / Phase 7 packaging / Phase 8 hybrid retrieval |\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:154:{\"command\": \"spec-realign\", \"status\": \"ok\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:162:{\"command\": \"spec-realign\", \"status\": \"ok\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:248:`/spec-inject` / `/spec-realign` は BM25 sparse search、raw chunk dense vector search、explicit target hint を RRF で fuse し、hit chunk を `source_spec_constraints` / `related_source_sections` の evidence に入れる。各 item は `excerpt` / `source_span` / `source_hash` / `retrieval_methods` / `ranking_score` を持つ。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:276:この checkout の `.spec-grag/config.toml` は、`[llm] provider = \"codex_cli\"` と Ollama `bge-m3` / `dimension = 1024` を使う。判断系 Codex model は Codex CLI catalog の slug `gpt-5.4`、Claude model は full Claude Code model name `claude-sonnet-4-6`、両 provider の既定 effort は `low` を設定している。抽出は provider 別に `[extraction.codex].model = \"gpt-5.4-mini\"`、`[extraction.claude].model = \"claude-haiku-4-5\"` を使い、`batch_size = 6` / `batch_max_chars = 4000` で複数 section を 1 prompt にまとめる。`section_max_heading_level = 4` により `####` までは section 化し、`#####` 以下は親 section 本文に統合する。Claude に切り替える場合は `[llm].provider` を `claude_cli` にする。旧 smoke 設定は `.spec-grag/config.smoke.toml` に退避しており、通常実行経路では使わない。既存 `.spec-grag/graph/` 生成物は過去 smoke の `stable_hash` metadata のため、production self project 評価では token 見積もり後に `spec-core --all` rebuild が必要である。小型一時 project の production probe では `spec-core --all` 56,425 tokens、no-change incremental 12,330 tokens、`spec-inject` 116,520 tokens、`spec-realign` 137,724 tokens を確認済み。repo-local `テスト用ドキュメント/**/*.md` 全体の full run はまだ未実施。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:282:Phase 5 では `AnswerSections` schema と固定 prompt を追加し、Answer provider を `codex` / `claude` / `template` から選べる境界にした。Phase 9 以降の production config では `[answer]` に stage 個別 provider を書かず、`[llm].provider` から `codex` / `claude` へ解決する。実 LLM 呼び出し時も `generate_realign_answer(task_prompt, injection_context, llm=...)` は project_root / path / raw source handle を受け取らない。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/HANDOFF.ja.md:284:Answer LLM が `needs_more_context=true` を返した場合、`/spec-realign` は `RealignResult` を生成せず `NeedMoreContextResult` / `blocked` に戻す。LLM が ConflictNotes / ReviewNotes を省略しても、renderer 側で必ず回答の「競合 / 不確実性 / 人間レビュー」区分に差し戻す。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE11_REPORT.ja.md:11:- `/spec-inject` / `/spec-realign` に `readiness_gate`、`retrieval`、`classification`、`answer_generation` を追加した。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE11_REPORT.ja.md:27:- `uv run --with pytest python -m pytest tests/test_cli.py tests/test_core_e2e.py tests/test_injection_realign.py tests/test_phase10_readiness.py -q`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/agent_doc/外部設計書リライト.md:203:7. /spec-realign の外部仕様\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/agent_doc/外部設計書リライト.md:228:| `/spec-realign` (内部実行: `spec-anchor realign`) | 必須 | 必須 |\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE8_REPORT.ja.md:10:`/spec-inject` / `/spec-realign` の source retrieval 主経路を、heading / section metadata の substring match から、raw document chunks + BM25 sparse lexical search + dense chunk vector search + graph expansion + rank fusion へ置き換えた。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE8_REPORT.ja.md:74:uv run --isolated --with pytest pytest tests/test_core_e2e.py tests/test_injection_realign.py -q\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE8_REPORT.ja.md:100:{\"command\": \"spec-realign\", \"status\": \"ok\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE8_REPORT.ja.md:120:uv run --isolated python -m spec_grag.slash spec-realign \\\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE8_REPORT.ja.md:138:`/spec-inject` / `/spec-realign` は次の順に候補を作る。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE1_REPORT.ja.md:18:- 経路 4: `/spec-realign`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE1_REPORT.ja.md:27:ただし、これは「完成版」ではなく「外部契約と主要境界が通る初期縦切り」である。特に `/spec-core` の graph 生成、`/spec-inject` の分類、`/spec-realign` の回答生成は、Phase 2 以降で本来設計の LLM extraction / GraphRAG retrieval / Classification / Answer LLM に置き換える前提である。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE1_REPORT.ja.md:36:- `/spec-core` / `/spec-inject` / `/spec-realign` の entrypoint を実装\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE1_REPORT.ja.md:81:未承認 Concept diff がある場合、`/spec-core` 通常実行、`/spec-inject`、`/spec-realign` は進めず `blocked` で停止する。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE1_REPORT.ja.md:110:### `/spec-realign`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE1_REPORT.ja.md:112:`/spec-realign` は `/spec-inject` 相当の context build を実行し、`context_ready=true` の場合だけ RealignResult を返す。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE1_REPORT.ja.md:132:「Answer 生成時に raw source を読まない」は運用ルールだけでは弱い。Phase 1 では `generate_realign_answer(task_prompt, injection_context)` のように、関数シグネチャ自体を `task_prompt + InjectionContext` だけにした。この形は Phase 5 の Answer LLM 化でも維持する。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE1_REPORT.ja.md:158:### `/spec-realign` の回答はテンプレート\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE1_REPORT.ja.md:209:- `tests/test_injection_realign.py`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE10_REPORT.ja.md:15:- `/spec-inject` / `/spec-realign` は readiness gate 経由になり、fresh artifact では同期 core 更新を行わない。local daily の dirty/stale/watcher running/queued は blocked、CI/smoke は foreground incremental、production は fail-fast。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE10_REPORT.ja.md:40:- `uv run --with pytest python -m pytest tests/test_cli.py tests/test_injection_realign.py tests/test_core_e2e.py tests/test_external_contract_e2e.py -q`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE4_REPORT.ja.md:63:- `tests/test_injection_realign.py`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE6_REPORT.ja.md:113:{\"command\": \"spec-realign\", \"status\": \"ok\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE6_REPORT.ja.md:119:uv run --isolated --with pytest pytest tests/test_phase6_operations.py tests/test_cli.py tests/test_cli_fixtures.py tests/test_injection_realign.py tests/test_concept_index.py tests/test_core_e2e.py -q\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE6_REPORT.ja.md:136:{\"command\": \"spec-realign\", \"status\": \"ok\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:40:- `uv run --with pytest python -m pytest tests/test_phase9_production_policy.py tests/test_phase12_hardening.py tests/test_injection_realign.py tests/test_phase7_packaging.py::test_template_resources_are_packaged_for_wheel_install -q`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:72:### spec-realign\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:74:- command: `spec-realign --task-prompt 'Scoped Store と Action runtime の設計上の制約を、根拠付きで簡潔に整理して'`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:83:- artifact: `.spec-grag/runs/20260502T080058.085853Z-spec-realign-32aa47a12a59.json`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:85:### spec-realign batch / cache 後\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:87:- command: `spec-realign --task-prompt 'Scoped Store と Action runtime の設計上の制約を、根拠付きで簡潔に整理して'`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:94:- artifact: `.spec-grag/runs/20260502T082150.417804Z-spec-realign-fd72d9ad2316.json`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:103:- answer generation latency: `spec-realign` では answer LLM が 40 秒台を占める\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:136:- `uv run --with pytest python -m pytest tests/test_concept_index.py tests/test_phase8_hybrid_retrieval.py tests/test_phase10_readiness.py::test_readiness_marks_old_concept_index_version_stale tests/test_phase12_hardening.py tests/test_realign_answer.py tests/test_phase9_production_policy.py tests/test_cli.py::test_cli_answer_failure_can_fallback_to_template -q` -> `58 passed in 15.68s`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:137:- `uv run --with pytest python -m pytest tests/test_realign_answer.py::test_answer_cache_key_ignores_volatile_runtime_metadata tests/test_realign_answer.py::test_answer_cache_round_trips_by_task_and_context -q` -> `2 passed in 2.32s`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE14_REPORT.ja.md:147:- Answer cache hit: `.spec-grag/runs/20260502T154702.759380Z-spec-realign-5aaef0f12cff.json`、answer `2.886ms`、answer LLM calls 0\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE5_REPORT.ja.md:4:> 対象: Phase 5 Answer LLM / `/spec-realign` 品質化\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE5_REPORT.ja.md:9:Phase 5 の目的である「`/spec-realign` の回答生成を、Answer phase isolation を維持したまま Answer LLM 化できる境界へ置き換える」は完了した。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE5_REPORT.ja.md:47:### `/spec-realign` の blocked 戻し\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE5_REPORT.ja.md:49:- `/spec-realign` は従来どおり `build_injection()` が `context_ready=true` を返すまで Answer を生成しない\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE5_REPORT.ja.md:62:- `tests/test_realign_answer.py`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE5_REPORT.ja.md:63:- `tests/test_injection_realign.py`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE5_REPORT.ja.md:72:- `/spec-realign` で Answer provider config 不正時に `failed` になること\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE5_REPORT.ja.md:80:`generate_realign_answer()` は引き続き `task_prompt` と `InjectionContext` だけを受け取る。provider config は CLI 側で adapter に変換し、Answer 関数には LLM object だけを渡すため、Answer phase に raw source read の入口を増やさずに済んだ。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE7_REPORT.ja.md:12:これにより fresh project に template を導入すると、`.spec-grag/config.toml`、`.codex/commands/spec-*.md`、Purpose / Concept 雛形を配置でき、同じ設定で `spec-core --all`、`spec-inject`、`spec-realign` の smoke が通る状態になった。\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE7_REPORT.ja.md:21:- `/spec-inject \"<task>\"`、`/spec-realign \"<task prompt>\"` の positional prompt を transport schema に変換できるようにした\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE7_REPORT.ja.md:34:- `templates/.codex/commands/spec-realign.md`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE7_REPORT.ja.md:85:- fresh project に setup した後、`spec-core --all` / `spec-inject` / `spec-realign` が通ること\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE7_REPORT.ja.md:108:{\"command\": \"spec-realign\", \"status\": \"ok\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE9_REPORT.ja.md:45:- `/spec-inject` / `/spec-realign` の context build 中に production provider が失敗した場合、CLI は `context_build_failed` の `ErrorResult` を返す\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE9_REPORT.ja.md:97:uv run --isolated --with pytest --with pydantic --with llama-index-core --with markdown-it-py pytest tests/test_phase7_packaging.py tests/test_cli.py tests/test_phase9_production_policy.py tests/test_injection_realign.py -q\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE9_REPORT.ja.md:114:spec-realign max_items=8: 11 turns / total 137,724 tokens / blocked NeedMoreContext\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE9_REPORT.ja.md:125:{\"command\": \"spec-realign\", \"status\": \"ok\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/PHASE9_REPORT.ja.md:134:spec_grag/templates/.codex/commands/spec-realign.md\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/BAK/DESIGN_DECISIONS.ja.md:59:| R-007 | `/spec-realign` は `/spec-inject` 相当の後に Answer を作る | 外部設計 6章 | `RealignResult = task_prompt + injection_context + answer` とし、Context を再定義しない | 採用済み |\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/BAK/DESIGN_DECISIONS.ja.md:60:| R-008 | `/spec-inject` と `/spec-realign` は最初に incremental 更新を行う | 外部設計 3.2, 5.3, 6.3 | 両コマンドの先頭に `/spec-core` 相当の incremental 処理を置く | 採用済み |\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/BAK/DESIGN_DECISIONS.ja.md:91:### 3.3 `/spec-realign`\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/BAK/DESIGN_DECISIONS.ja.md:95:| C-REAL-001 | `/spec-realign` は `/spec-inject` と同じ手順で `InjectionContext` を作る | 採用済み | 外部設計 6.3 | `/spec-realign` flow |\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/BAK/DESIGN_DECISIONS.ja.md:240:4. `/spec-realign` の内部設計を書く\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/AUDIT_TODO.ja.md:34:6. E2E / GRAG 品質監査: build 済み graph を使って injection / realign / retrieval 品質を見る\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/full-grag-2026-05-05/doc/AUDIT_TODO.ja.md:92:  - `spec-realign`: exit 0、elapsed `99.899s`、`status=degraded`、`context_ready=true`、`llm_calls=10`、answer 生成まで完了、warning `classification_incomplete`（Phase 14 前の historical / stale）\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/archive/f