cedure says I should stop and not format an answer when the config is not found.\\n\\nLet me follow the procedure strictly and report the issue.\\n\\nBut I should also check if there's a spec-anchor project at a different location that might cover the ec-spoke.local project - perhaps in a parent directory with the config.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":1,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":457,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":47782,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":457},\"output_tokens\":8,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"diagnostics\":null,\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"c5976bea-db53-4952-a093-280a919f4f68\",\"uuid\":\"b5c2da9a-9251-4e50-b594-f8029ae3838a\",\"request_id\":\"req_011CbHrRZ4F9fuJXq1xP94ZB\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-002300-codex-e2e-slash-skill/stdout/claude-slash-spec-realign-clean-tmp.stdout:491:{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":0,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"thinking_delta\",\"thinking\":\" `/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/.spec-anchor` but that's for the spec-anchor project itself.\\n\\nAccording to the spec-realign error handling procedure:\\n>\"}},\"session_id\":\"c5976bea-db53-4952-a093-280a919f4f68\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"ab04627c-d8be-446e-86aa-522184b06bec\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-002300-codex-e2e-slash-skill/stdout/claude-slash-spec-realign-clean-tmp.stdout:506:{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_011XsxBgBQNkrA8MypzeH3JR\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"There's no `.spec-anchor` set up for the ec-spoke.local project. The spec-anchor CLI exists at `/home/kazuki/public_htm