me/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-010512-codex-e2e-f002-retest/stdout/claude-slash-spec-realign.stdout:8:{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":0,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"thinking_delta\",\"thinking\":\" user is invoking `/spec-realign` with the argument \\\"認証セッションとCSRFの仕様に従って、ログイン後セッ\"}},\"session_id\":\"c9429e1e-7c93-460a-a235-2565e60843da\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"deb9568f-9f71-4bb5-803c-27fe6bb37ad6\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-010512-codex-e2e-f002-retest/stdout/claude-slash-spec-realign.stdout:21:{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":0,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"thinking_delta\",\"thinking\":\" I'm going to hand this off to an agent to execute the full spec-realign workflow.\"}},\"session_id\":\"c9429e1e-7c93-460a-a235-2565e60843da\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"ae4a9729-e105-45a2-ade7-3b79fb4bfcbc\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-010512-codex-e2e-f002-retest/stdout/claude-slash-spec-realign.stdout:23:{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01H7hGxxiqpGsWpyp1pa7MjL\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"thinking\",\"thinking\":\"The user is invoking `/spec-realign` with the argument \\\"認証セッションとCSRFの仕様に従って、ログイン後セッションと状態変更リクエストの扱いを回答して\\\". \\n\\nLet me follow the mandatory steps:\\n\\n1. Define the task from the argument and conversation context\\n2. Generate search keys\\n3. Perform Agentic Search (4 paths: inject-search + inject-section, inject-chapters, inject-purpose, inject-conflicts)\\n4. Build constraints JSON\\n5. Self-check constraints\\n6. Build answer candidate\\n7. Format with 4 sections\\n\\n\\n8. Run `spec-anchor realign --answer-json '<json>'`\\n9. Present formatted result\\n\\nThe task centers on authentication session and CSRF specifications, focusing on how to handle post-login sessions and state-changing requests. I need to check if the config file exists in the current working directory, then proceed with the agentic search using key terms like session management, CSRF protection, login session handling, and state change request handling.\\n\\nNow I'm going to hand this off to an agent to execute the full spec-realign workflow.\",\"signature\":\"\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":11424,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":13470,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":11424},\"output_tokens\":8,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"diagnostics\":null,\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"c9429e1e-7c93-460a-a235-2565e60843da\",\"uuid\":\"ab4b13ef-1f83-48d3-b6d4-86ae04fcd7ee\",\"request_id\":\"req_011CbHtnyNYK2aV8f1zG9RWR\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-010512-codex-e2e-f002-retest/stdout/claude-slash-spec-realign.stdout:27:{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":1,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"text_delta\",\"text\":\"/spec-realign` を実行します。まず `.spec-anchor/config.toml` の存在確認と4パスの\"}},\"session_id\":\"c9429e1e-7c93-460a-a235-2565e60843da\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"d4bd5a92-b23e-4b12-aac7-6a3cc0f39b24\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-010512-codex-e2e-f002-retest/stdout/claude-slash-spec-realign.stdout:29:{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01H7hGxxiqpGsWpyp1pa7MjL\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"`/spec-realign` を実行します。まず `.spec-anchor/config.toml` の存在確認と4パスの Agentic Search を行います。\"}],\"stop_reason\":null,\"stop_sequence\":null,\"stop_details\":null,\"usage\":{\"input_tokens\":3,\"cache_creation_input_tokens\":11424,\"cache_read_input_tokens\":13470,\"cache_creation\":{\"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens\":0,\"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens\":11424},\"output_tokens\":8,\"service_tier\":\"standard\",\"inference_geo\":\"not_available\"},\"diagnostics\":null,\"context_management\":null},\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"session_id\":\"c9429e1e-7c93-460a-a235-2565e60843da\",\"uuid\":\"6d2901c3-a71a-46ba-8b2c-1ac7e65ca64e\",\"request_id\":\"req_011CbHtnyNYK2aV8f1zG9RWR\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-010512-codex-e2e-f002-retest/stdout/claude-slash-spec-realign.stdout:34:{\"type\":\"stream_event\",\"event\":{\"type\":\"content_block_delta\",\"index\":2,\"delta\":{\"type\":\"input_json_delta\",\"partial_json\":\"-realign 4パスのAgentic Search\"}},\"session_id\":\"c9429e1e-7c93-460a-a235-2565e60843da\",\"parent_tool_use_id\":null,\"uuid\":\"f32a9733-ed49-47b8-9830-567414f5b73e\"}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-010512-codex-e2e-f002-retest/stdout/claude-slash-spec-realign.stdout:58:{\"type\":\"assistant\",\"message\":{\"model\":\"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\"id\":\"msg_01H7hGxxiqpGsWpyp1pa7MjL\",\"type\":\"message\",\"role\":\"assistant\",\"content\":[{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"id\":\"toolu_01TRfDvc4Lja3xw45pNZGLhJ\",\"name\":\"Agent\",\"input\":{\"description\":\"spec-realign 4パスのAgentic Search\",\"prompt\":\"\\nあなたは spec-anchor プロジェクトの仕様書検索エージェントです。\\n作業ディレクトリ: /tmp/spec-anchor-codex-e2e-f002-retest.N4Lyjy\\n\\n## タスク\\n「認証セッションとCSRFの仕様に従って、ログイン後セッションと状態変更リクエストの扱いを回答して」という課題に対して、\\nspec-anchor CLI の inject-* コマンドを使って4パスの Agentic Search を実行してください。\\n\\n## 手順\\n\\n**Step 0: config 確認**\\n```\\ncat /tmp/spec-anchor-codex-e2e-f002-retest.N4Lyjy/.spec-anchor/config.toml\\n```\\nが存在しない場合は「config.toml not found」とだけ報告して終了してください。\\n\\n**Step 1: search keys を生成**\\n課題から以下の search keys を使います:\\n- \\\"session management\\\"\\n- \\\"CSRF\\\"\\n- \\\"login\\\"\\n- \\\"authentication\\\"\\n- \\\"