",\"text\":\"The source spec has the relevant auth terms, but I still need the CLI-mediated evidence path and `realign` pass. I’ll run the four inject paths, then feed the structured answer through `realign` using an external file descriptor so the project files remain untouched.\"}}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-010512-codex-e2e-f002-retest/stdout/codex-skill-f003.stdout:54:{\"type\":\"item.completed\",\"item\":{\"id\":\"item_28\",\"type\":\"agent_message\",\"text\":\"The exact source lines confirm the two requested constraints and there are no resolved conflict items. I’m doing the final `realign` pass through an external answer file path now, then I’ll summarize it in the skill’s required sections with explicit empty sections.\"}}\n/home/kazuki/public_html/spec-anchor/doc/e2eテストCODEX実施用/evidence/20260523-010512-codex-e2e-f002-retest/stdout/claude-slash-spec-inject-f003.stdout:3:{\"type\":\"system\",\"subtype\":\"init\",\"cwd\":\"/tmp/spec-anchor-codex-e2e-f002-retest.N4Lyjy\",\"session_id\":\"8ec58f15-3081-4aed-bfdc-e5a2feb0380b\",\"tools\":[\"Task\",\"AskUserQuestion\",\"Bash\",\"CronCreate\",\"CronDelete\",\"CronList\",\"Edit\",\"EnterPlanMode\",\"EnterWorktree\",\"ExitPlanMode\",\"ExitWorktree\",\"Glob\",\"Grep\",\"Monitor\",\"NotebookEdit\",\"PushNotification\",\"Read\",\"RemoteTrigger\",\"ScheduleWakeup\",\"ShareOnboardingGuide\",\"Skill\",\"TaskCreate\",\"TaskGet\",\"TaskList\",\"TaskOutput\",\"TaskStop\",\"TaskUpdate\",\"ToolSearch\",\"WebFetch\",\"WebSearch\",\"Write\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Gmail__authenticate\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Gmail__complete_authentication\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Google_Calendar__authenticate\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Google_Calendar__complete_authentication\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Google_Drive__authenticate\",\"mcp__claude_ai_Google_Drive__complete_authentication\"],\"mcp_servers\":[{\"name\":\"claude.ai Google Drive\",\"status\":\"needs-auth\"},{\"name\":\"claude.ai Google Calendar\",\"status\":\"needs-auth\"},